com.ikalagaming.plugins.events

  • Packages that use com.ikalagaming.plugins.events 
    Package Description
    com.ikalagaming.plugins
    Manages plugins, which are distinct subsystems of the engine that can be dynamically swapped in and out or enabled/disabled during runtime.
  • Classes in com.ikalagaming.plugins.events used by com.ikalagaming.plugins 
    Class and Description
    PluginDisabled
    Fired when (after) a plugin is disabled.
    PluginEnabled
    Fired when (after) a plugin is enabled.
    PluginLoaded
    Fired when (after) a plugin is loaded.
